headline: RH (RH) Misses Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: RH (RH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -17.28% and 1.80%, respectively, for the quarter ended January 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
